ygData.messageBody:
I am currently level 34, and I am almost level 35. Without getting into the debate about whether Wizards should or should not solo, does anyone know if I can solo the dwarves at the BB dock at level 35? I have killed them in a group and I have seen level 35 pet classes soloing them, but I am not sure if a wizzie can solo them at 35. Anyone soloed them at 35? If not, has anyone soloed them? If so, what level?

Thanks,

Gantorek Ttefabob of Clan Cathar on the Povar Server
